procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFAmountWithCalculatedCurrency) var AnnualInterest : Num8 var debug : Pointer var BillLinePeriod : Num8 var InterestOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnQuater : Num8 var MonthOnSemiAnnual : Num8 var MonthOnAnnual : Num8 var BeginDate : tWFDate var EndDate : tWFDate var BillLineAmount : Num8
MonthOnQuater = 3.0 MonthOnSemiAnnual = 6.0 MonthOnAnnual = 12.0 AnnualInterest = 0.07 ; ;debug = Risky.OpenDebug ; BillLineAmount = self.BillLine__BaseAmount BeginDate = self.BillLine__EffectiveDate EndDate = self.BillLine__EndDate MonthOnPeriod = self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, EndDate) ; Result = 0 if not self.DateIsNull(EndDate) if MonthOnPeriod < 1 ; Monthly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 12.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate)) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if MonthOnPeriod < MonthOnQuater ; Quaterly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 4.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnQuater) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if MonthOnPeriod < MonthOnSemiAnnual ; Semi-Annually InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 2.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnSemiAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else ; Annually InterestOnPeriod = AnnualInterest Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount endIf endIf endIf endIf endProc

;Result = Coverage__CoverageAmount / 10 ;if Coverage__Classifications__WaiverofPremium = With ; Result = Result * 1.2 ;endIf ; ; Elimination period ratings (only precisely defined for 30, 60 & 90) if self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _0 EliminationPeriodRate = 1.3 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _7 EliminationPeriodRate = 1.2 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _14 EliminationPeriodRate = 1.1 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _30 EliminationPeriodRate = 1 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _60 EliminationPeriodRate = 0.75 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__ShortTermEliminationPeriod = _90 EliminationPeriodRate = 0.4 endIf ; SmokerRate = 1.25 ; ; Basis premium Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount / 12 * self.Disability_PremiumRatefromCoverageAmount(self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) ; ; Elimination period ratings Result = Result * EliminationPeriodRate ; ; Female ratings if self.Subscriber__Gender = gFemale Result = Result * self.Disability_Femalerate(self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endIf ; ; Occupational Class ratings Result = Result * self.Disability_OccupationnalClassRate(self.Insured__Classifications__OccupationalClass) ; ; Smoker status ratings if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = Smoker Result = Result * SmokerRate endIf ; ; WOP ratings if self.Coverage__Classifications__WaiverofPremium = With Result = Result * 1.2 endIf endProc

; ; Elimination period ratings (only precisely defined for 60, 90 & 180) if self.Coverage__Classifications__LongTermEliminationPeriod = _60 EliminationPeriodRate = 1 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__LongTermEliminationPeriod = _90 EliminationPeriodRate = 0.75 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__LongTermEliminationPeriod = _180 EliminationPeriodRate = 0.4 elseif self.Coverage__Classifications__LongTermEliminationPeriod = _365 EliminationPeriodRate = 0.3 endIf ; SmokerRate = 1.25 ; ; Basis premium Result = self.Coverage__CoverageAmount / 12 * self.Disability_PremiumRatefromCoverageAmount(self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) ; ; Elimination period ratings Result = Result * EliminationPeriodRate ; ; Female ratings if self.Subscriber__Gender = gFemale Result = Result * self.Disability_Femalerate(self.Subscriber__Age__Exact) endIf ; ; Occupational Class ratings Result = Result * self.Disability_OccupationnalClassRate(self.Insured__Classifications__OccupationalClass) ; ; Smoker status ratings if self.Insured__Classifications__SmokerStatus = Smoker Result = Result * SmokerRate endIf ; ; WOP ratings if self.Coverage__Classifications__WaiverofPremium = With Result = Result * 1.2 endIf endProc

procedure WFCalculate(inOut Result : tWFAmountWithCalculatedCurrency) var AnnualInterest : Num8 var debug : Pointer var BillLinePeriod : Num8 var InterestOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnPeriod : Num8 var MonthOnQuater : Num8 var MonthOnSemiAnnual : Num8 var MonthOnAnnual : Num8 var BeginDate : tWFDate var EndDate : tWFDate var BillLineAmount : Num8
MonthOnQuater = 3.0 MonthOnSemiAnnual = 6.0 MonthOnAnnual = 12.0 AnnualInterest = 0.07 ; ;debug = Risky.OpenDebug ; BillLineAmount = self.BillLine__BaseAmount BeginDate = self.BillLine__EffectiveDate EndDate = self.BillLine__EndDate MonthOnPeriod = self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, EndDate) ; Result = 0 if not self.DateIsNull(EndDate) if MonthOnPeriod < 1 ; Monthly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 12.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate)) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if MonthOnPeriod < MonthOnQuater ; Quaterly InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 4.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnQuater) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else if MonthOnPeriod < MonthOnSemiAnnual ; Semi-Annually InterestOnPeriod = self.Power(1 + AnnualInterest, 1.0 / 2.0) - 1 Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnSemiAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount else ; Annually InterestOnPeriod = AnnualInterest Result = self.BillLine__BaseAmount * self.Power(1 + InterestOnPeriod, self.NumberOfMonthBetweenTwoDates(BeginDate, self.CurrentDate) / MonthOnAnnual) - self.BillLine__BaseAmount endIf endIf endIf endIf endProc
